Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBWasteLocationReporting

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commander4j.db.JDBWasteLocationReporting
  • public class JDBWasteLocationReporting
extends java.lang.Object
    The JDBWasteLocationReporting class updates the table APP_WASTE_LOCATION_REPORTING. This table contains a single row for each unique Waste Transaction Type as stored in the APP_WASTE_LOCATION_REPORTING table.

    See Also:
    JDBWasteReasons, JDBWasteReportingIDS, JDBWasteTransactionType, JDBWasteLocationReporting, JDBWasteTypes, JDBWasteMaterial, JDBWasteLog
